%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to guarantee"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to insure"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to vouch"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to have insured"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to ensure, to guarantee","examples":[{"text":"كي نضمِّن أن توصلنا قراراتنا في المجالات الأخلاقية إلى نتائج جيدة، لا نقدر أن نتَّكل فقط على إحساسنا أو رأي الآخرين.","english":"In order to ensure that our decisions in ethical areas lead to good results, we cannot rely solely on our own feelings or the opinions of others."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to embed"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to insert, to include"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"inside, interior"},{"pos":"prep","gloss":"inside, within, among"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Adverbial accusative of ضِمْن (ḍimn)."},"ipa":["/dˤa.mi.na/","/dˤam.ma.na/","/dˤimn/","/dˤim.na/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n26042","headword_ar":"ضِمْنٌ","root":"Dmn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaY~","text_ar":"طَىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, MA, K,) i. e. the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inside,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA, TK,) [lit. the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"folding,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of a writing, or letter. (S, MA, K, TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anofa*otuhu Dimona","text_ar":"اَنْفَذْتُهُ ضِمْنَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kitaAbiY","text_ar":"كِتَابِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY Tay~ihi","text_ar":"فِى طَيِّهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I sent it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"transmitted it, within the folding of my writing"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"letter;"},{"kind":"text","text":"mean-"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1805},{"kind":"text","text":"ing"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"infolded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"enclosed, in it; included in it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the inside of it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY Dimoni","text_ar":"فِى ضِمْنِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kalaAmihi","text_ar":"كَلَامِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kitaAbihi","text_ar":"كِتَابِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Among the contents,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"implications, of his speech"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of his writing"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"letter"},{"kind":"text","text":"] ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fY maTaAwiyhi","text_ar":"فى مَطَاوِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"); and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the indications thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing that satisfies the stomach:"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^agonaY Ean~iY fulaAnN DimonFA","text_ar":"مَا اَغْنَى عَنِّى فُلَانٌ ضِمْنًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one did not stand me in stead,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"supply my want, of anything, even as much as a thing that would satisfy the stomach."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","MA","K","TK"]},{"entry_id":"n26043","headword_ar":"ضَمَنٌ","root":"Dmn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DamaAnN","text_ar":"ضَمَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DamaAnapN","text_ar":"ضَمَانَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A malady of long continuance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as cripples;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an affliction in the body,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by some trial,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fracture,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other ailment;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DumonapN","text_ar":"ضُمْنَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same; (K;) and ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"simply"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a disease,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"malady;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAnato","text_ar":"كَانَتْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dumonapu fulaAnK A^arobaEapa A^a$ohurK","text_ar":"ضُمْنَةُ فُلَانٍ اَرْبَعَةَ اَشْهُرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The disease of such a one was four months"},{"kind":"text","text":"in duration]. (S, TA.) [See also 1, last two sentences.] ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DamanN","text_ar":"ضَمَنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A burden;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kal~N","text_ar":"كَلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": so in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DamanN EalaY A^aSoHaAbihi","text_ar":"ضَمَنٌ عَلَى اَصْحَابِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is a burden upon his companions"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (AZ, TA.)       -A2-  It is also an epithet: see the next pargaraph."}],"source_refs":["S","K","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n26044","headword_ar":"ضَمِنٌ","root":"Dmn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(applied to a man, S) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Affected with a malady of long continuance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as cripples;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"afflicted in the body,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by some trial,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fracture,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other ailment:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DamanN","text_ar":"ضَمَنٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies [the same; or simply]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affected with a disease,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"malady;"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a man [and to two and more and to a female; being originally an inf. n.]; having no dual nor pl. nor fem. form: (TA:) pl. of the former"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DamonaY","text_ar":"ضَمْنَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * Msb, K, * TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Daminuwna","text_ar":"ضَمِنُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or the former of these is pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DamiynN","text_ar":"ضَمِينٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaminN","text_ar":"ضَمِنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aikotataba DaminFA","text_ar":"اِكْتَتَبَ ضَمِنًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DamanFA","text_ar":"ضَمَنًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"] means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He wrote himself down"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as one affected with a malady of long continuance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the register of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DamonaY","text_ar":"ضَمْنَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zamonaY","text_ar":"زَمْنَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K, TA;) i. e. he asked that he might write himself down [as such], and took for himself a billet from the commander of the army in order to excuse himself from fighting against the unbelievers: (TA:) of such it is said that God will raise him in that state on the day of resurrection. (S, TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEobuwTapN gayoru DaminapK","text_ar":"مَعْبُوطَةٌ غَيْرُ ضَمِنَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", occurring in a trad., means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Slaughtered not having any disease."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  Also (tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Loving:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DamaAnapN","text_ar":"ضَمَانَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"loving excessively,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"admiringly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","TA"]}]}}